API - Create GET API to Fetch All Active Life & Disability Band Overrides



Key details
Description


As an Administrator, I want an API to retrieve all active Life & Disability band override records So that users can view existing overrides in the Admin App grid.  Acceptance Criteria
AC1 – Fetch Active Overrides
Given a valid GET request is made When the API GET api-bss/v1.0/benefits/{companyId}/{employeeId}/life-dis-band-overrides is invoked Then the system retrieves all active override records from the database And returns them in the expected response format

AC2 
Given the endpoint is called When the controller method executes Then:
	•	lifeDisabilityBandOverrideService.findAllActive() is called
	•	The result is returned directly

AC3 
Given the service throws a anyRuntimeException When the endpoint is called Then:
	•	The exception is not handled in controller
	•	It propagates as-is

AC4 – Empty Response Handling
Given no active records exist When the API is invoked Then the system returns an empty list with HTTP 200 response

